## 📊 수집할 메트릭

### 실시간 메트릭 (1초마다)

```
1. 노드별 상태:
   - Node ID
   - Current term
   - Current leader
   - Log length
   - Commit index
   - Applied index

2. 성능 지표:
   - Message latency (Leader → Follower)
   - Election timeout count
   - Heartbeat count

3. 리소스 사용:
   - Memory RSS (MB)
   - Goroutine count
   - CPU usage (%)
```

### 체크포인트 기록 (각 Phase 끝)

```
Phase 1: Initial state
  - All nodes up and healthy
  - Leader elected

Phase 2: Normal operation
  - Replication latency: X ms
  - Memory baseline: Y MB

Phase 3: Network partition
  - Partition created
  - Node 3 isolated

Phase 4: Split operation
  - Partition A: Leader active
  - Partition B: Read-only mode

Phase 5: Recovery
  - Network restored
  - Replication resumed
  - Recovery time: Z sec

Phase 6: Final state
  - All logs consistent
  - All nodes healthy
  - Memory cleanup: OK/LEAK
```

